headline: Accenture price target lowered to $365 from $394 at TD Cowen
summary: TD Cowen lowered the firm’s price target on Accenture (ACN) to $365 from $394 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm said the company acknowledged the obvious in Fed procurement pressure amid DOGE; the extent of impact is still a finger in wind, but headwind nonetheless. The rest of its business remains unchanged to date. Published first on TheFly – the ultimate source for real-time, market-moving breaking financial news.
